sing complex, Rabi Rashmi Abasan in West Bengal on Tuesday. The two met Environment Minister Jairam Ramesh on Wednesday to discuss how a global deal could be struck at Copenhagen.\u000a\u000a... contd.\u000a\u000aALSO READ Narendra Modi a monster, Trinamool has pact with him: Buddha\u000a\u000aPlease read our terms of use before posting comments
