othing else is going to happen,\ufffd\ufffd\ufffd Mr de Boer said.\u000a\u000a\u000a\u000aMr Boer said not many countries wanted a new treaty and there was dissatisfaction among the developing nations over financial management by international institutions. They had put the funding proposals before the developed nations but not much has moved forward.
