iculture, water, health and forest by studying the four crucial regions viz., western ghats, northeast, Himalayan ecosystem and the coastal system, before presenting a report in November.\u000a\u000aPlanning Commission member K. Kasturi Rangan inaugurated the Lower Atmospheric Wind Profiling (LAWP) radar. ISRO Chairman K. Radhakrishnan and NARL Director A. Jayaraman explained the various ongoing projects to the Minister.
